cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.MM

The paper proposes a new deep convolutional network for fingerprint minutiae extraction, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the representation ability of deep learning, which suggests a possible connection to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper deals with image segmentation and enhancement, which could be related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the proposed algorithm compared to state-of-the-art methods, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
